  "keyFeatures": [
    "FastMCP server exposing 11 corpus query tools to AI assistants (Claude, GPT, etc.)",
    "Support for Bible (BHSA, GNT), Quran, Tanakh, commentaries, lexicons, and dictionaries",
    "Graph-based annotated text queries using Context-Fabric (fork of Text-Fabric)",
    "EPUB and HTML to Text-Fabric dataset converters for importing custom books",
    "Git-based corpus dataset fetching (shallow clone + TF directory discovery)",
    "Multi-corpus support with named corpora and cursor-based search pagination",
    "SSE, streamable HTTP, and stdio transport modes for different client types",
    "Supabase-backed authentication with anonymous, email OTP, and OIDC (Apple/Google) flows",
    "Pydantic-settings configuration with per-environment .env files",
    ".exg packaging format for distributable corpus bundles"
  ],
